			<action-date date="20130718">July 18, 2013</action-date>
			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="H001067">Mr. Hudson</sponsor> (for
			 himself, <cosponsor name-id="M001157">Mr. McCaul</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="T000193">Mr. Thompson of Mississippi</cosponsor>, and
			 <cosponsor name-id="R000588">Mr. Richmond</cosponsor>) introduced the following
